  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study was to compare the response to cardiac resynchronization therapy when
      the interventricular pacing interval was optimized by Tissue Doppler Imaging (TDI) to
      response when it was optimized following QRS width criteria.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
  <phase>Phase 3</phase>
